# Bible versions + original-language data — copyright guard (v1.0.3~).
# Only copyright-clean data is tracked / redistributed:
#   · KRV.SQLite3      개역한글 (대한성서공회, 저작재산권 만료 — royalty-free)
#   · 개역한글S.sdb     KRV + Strong's tags (자체 원어 엔진의 기반)
#   · KJV+.SQLite3     KJV 1769 + Strong's numbers (public domain) — 영어 원전 분해 + 동봉
#   · HebGrkEn.dct     BDB(1906)+Strong's(1890) — public domain. (tracked, but
#                      EXCLUDED from builds; users opt-in as an external module)
# Everything else is copyrighted (ESV/NKJV/KNRSV/NRKV/myJB bibles, TWOT-Korean
# HebGrkKo.dct). Kept LOCALLY for the maintainer but NOT tracked or shipped;
# end users drop their own licensed modules into these folders.
BethlehemWin/
bible_versions/*
!bible_versions/KRV.SQLite3
!bible_versions/KJV+.SQLite3
!bible_versions/aliases_override.example.json
original_lang/*
!original_lang/개역한글S.sdb
!original_lang/HebGrkEn.dct

# 사용자 읽기 글꼴 폴더 — 사용자가 넣는 .ttf/.otf 는 추적하지 않고 안내만 동봉
fonts/*
!fonts/README.txt

# Mac source package (assembled artifact, contains data)
AutoBible-mac-source.zip
